texts.text: There you are, woman.
We meet again, Rahab.
I never expected we'd reunite in our own world.
I also think this to be premature.
However, my underlings' invasion of this world is sluggish.
Thanks to you stubborn humans, I must clear the way myself.
I shall start with you first, woman.
For striking my inverted scale, I'll deal with you personally.
Very well. I accept your challenge.
Yo, Rahab. Mind if we join the fray?
Rika is our comrade. We ain't leaving her to fight alone.
Foolish humans. Your numbers are meaningless.
Come forth. I'll crush you all the same.
Okay, but don't cry foul later!
Let's go! Devil Download!
Devil Download!
Let's settle this, Rahab!
>The fight is on as Rahab enters our world!
>The Liberators surround the massive Rahab and attack.
Join me, Shiang!
Understood! Let's do it!
>Jeng Yun and Shiang Sun's allies launch a simultaneous assault.
>However...
Die, impudent humans.
>Rahab's giant tail blows their demonic allies back.
Ngh! This demon is truly powerful.
Fighting him with just the two of us is definitely reckless.
Even so, everyone is together now!
Exactly! If two people can't do the trick, we'll get four!
Yep! And if that ain't enough, we'll get eight or even ten!
Let's join together and show this lizard who's boss!
Understood!
You think you stand a chance against me? How naive.
I'll break that spirit soon enough.
>The battle between Rahab and the Liberators escalates.
>Rahab uses his size to unleash a series of knockout blows.
>Meanwhile, the Liberators run circles around Rahab.
>The fight drags on as neither lands a decisive blow, but...
>The situation quickly shifts.
Vince! Look at the sky!
That's...
>A host of humanoid figures descend in a flash of light.
>They are...
Well done, humans.
We shall aid you. There is no question Rahab will fall here.
Act as our support. That is your role.
A Divine army...
These guys are killin' me!
Hey, way to steal our thunder.
You appear at last, Divine.
I once fell into your trap and had no choice but to flee.
However, that resentment has become my strength.
Allow me to demonstrate it on you.
Prepare yourselves, humans, and follow our lead.
Should we?
Fine.
...I ain't thrilled, but let's play nice for now.
...Yeah. I ain't too happy about it though.
Yeah, it'll be tough to take down Rahab without them.
Gotta pick and choose our battles.
Yes, understood!
*Trumpet*
Say your prayers, Rahab.
>With the Liberators' aid, the Divine launch an attack.
>Their mighty weapons pierce Rahab's hard scales.
Gah!
Incredible... They slashed his scales with ease.
Is he all bark and no bite...?
Rahab, you shall once again yield to us Divine.
And this time, there is no escape.
You dare presume I would flee...?
Keh-keh-keh...
What is so funny?
Do not underestimate me, angels.
>Rahab opens wide and devours the angels in front of him.
Ugh, you all taste vile.
Still, I'll eat every last one of you to satisfy my rage.
...You have grown stronger yet still evil incarnate.
We shall take the offensive and spread out to overwhelm him.
Hey, wait! I'd be more careful if I were you!
He's right! If you spread out too farâ€”
Save your breath. We needn't heed the advice of mere tools.
Continue to assist us from the sidelines.
Tch!
It's no use, Megakin. At any rate, right now...!
I know, I know! We'll support the angels' offensive!
You are the last course.
Gah!
>Rahab consumes the Divine one by one.
>And now, the last has been devoured.
I win, you accursed Divine.
The angels have been wiped out...
Shit! Why'd they rush in like that?!
If they'd been more cooperative with us, then I'm sure...
This is no time to freak out!
Things are tight, but Rahab is worn out! We gotta strike NOW!
Yes, I agree!
For the sake of the people, we cannot afford to lose!
Enough, humans. I've lost the will to fight.
What...?
